{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"z2-quiz-2","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"专题集训","title":"专题集训二 第2题","difficulty":3,"tags":["有理数","绝对值"],"content":"若 $|a - 2|$ 与 $|b + 4|$ 互为相反数，则 $a + b$ 的值为______。","steps":[{"title":"解答","content":"由 $|a - 2| + |b + 4| = 0$\n得 $a - 2 = 0$，$b + 4 = 0$\n$a = 2$，$b = -4$\n$a + b = -2$","formula":"a + b = -2"}]},"id":"z2-quiz-2"},"__N_SSG":true}